The paper discusses the distribution of PageRank mass in a web graph, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SOC). The use of singular perturbation approach suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of scientific computing (cs.SI) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the study of dead-ends and the choice of damping factor may relate to cybersecurity (cs.CYBER).
